  "text": "In this study, we established a rat model of SAP to determine whether the DCQD could alleviate the systemic inflammatory response and intestinal injury associated with SAP via regulating JAK2-STAT3 signaling pathway. Our findings indicate that DCQD ameliorated inflammatory cytokines and intestinal injury in rats with SAP, which may be closely associated with the inhibition of the JAK2/STAT3 signaling pathway. SAP is an inflammatory disease with variable involvement of the pancreas and/or remote organ systems and with the development of a systemic inflammatory response [CITATION_1] .",
